        <!-- ========================= Pluswealth PMS (moved) start ========================= -->
        <section id="pluswealth" class="pt-60 pb-60">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xl-10 col-lg-10 mx-auto">
                        <div class="section-title text-center mb-55">
                            <h2 class="mb-20 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".2s">Pluswealth PMS</h2>
                            <p class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".4s">Discover PlusWealth PMS: our philosophy, risk management approach, suitability and practical details.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Row 1: What is PlusWealth PMS -->
                <div class="row align-items-center mb-60">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay=".2s">
                        <div class="overview-img text-center">
                            <img src="assets/img/feature-2.svg" alt="What is PlusWealth PMS" style="max-width:360px">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay=".4s">
                        <h3>What is PlusWealth PMS</h3>
                        <p>PlusWealth PMS is a rule-based portfolio management service that combines systematic signals, disciplined risk controls, and dynamic asset allocation to pursue steady compounding over market cycles.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Row 2: Investment philosophy (image right) -->
                <div class="row align-items-center mb-60">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2 wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay=".2s">
                        <div class="overview-img text-center">
                            <img src="assets/img/feature-3.svg" alt="Investment philosophy" style="max-width:360px">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1 wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay=".4s">
                        <h3>Our investment philosophy</h3>
                        <p>We favor evidence-based, repeatable rules over discretion. Diversification across assets and factors, combined with regime-aware risk controls, helps us target consistent returns while limiting downside.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Row 3: How we manage risk (image left) -->
                <div class="row align-items-center mb-60">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay=".2s">
                        <div class="overview-img text-center">
                            <img src="assets/img/about-img.svg" alt="How we manage risk" style="max-width:360px">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay=".4s">
                        <h3>How we manage risk</h3>
                        <p>Risk is managed via regime detection, position sizing limits, stop/overlay rules, and continuous stress-testing. Tactical hedges and liquidity buffers are used when downside risk rises.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Row 4: Why rule-based investing (image right) -->
                <div class="row align-items-center mb-60">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2 wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay=".2s">
                        <div class="overview-img text-center">
                            <img src="assets/img/feature-1.svg" alt="Why rule-based investing" style="max-width:360px">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1 wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay=".4s">
                        <h3>Why rule-based investing</h3>
                        <p>Rules reduce behavioral biases and improve consistency. By codifying decisions we can backtest, measure, and improve strategies while ensuring disciplined execution.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Row 5: Who this PMS is suitable for & practicals -->
                <div class="row align-items-center mb-60">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay=".2s">
                        <h3>Who this PMS is suitable for</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Investors seeking long-term capital growth with downside protection</li>
                            <li>Those comfortable with a multi-year horizon</li>
                            <li>Clients who prefer transparent, rule-based processes</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay=".4s">
                        <h3>Minimum investment & regulatory details</h3>
                        <p>Minimum investment and regulatory specifics vary by product and jurisdiction. Typically, minimums start at INR 10,00,000; assets are held with regulated custodians and the PMS operates under applicable regulatory frameworks. Contact us for the definitive product brochure and compliance documents.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
