                                        <td>-3.2%</td>
                                        <td>-6.9%</td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                        <p><strong>Benchmark comparison</strong> — Fusion aims to outperform a blended benchmark (equities + bonds / risk parity proxy) on a risk-adjusted basis, with lower drawdown during adverse regimes.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 4.4 Fusion – FAQs -->
                <div class="row mb-80">
                    <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                        <h3 class="mb-15">4.4 Fusion – FAQs</h3>
                        <div class="faq-list" id="fusionFaq">
                            <div class="faq-item mb-3">
                                <button class="faq-toggle btn btn-link d-flex align-items-center" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#faq1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq1">
                                    <span class="faq-icon mr-3">+</span>
                                    <strong>Minimum investment</strong>
                                </button>
                                <div id="faq1" class="collapse" data-parent="#fusionFaq">
                                    <div class="card card-body">Typically depends on the product variant; contact us for current minimums. (Placeholder: INR 10,00,000)</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="faq-item mb-3">
                                <button class="faq-toggle btn btn-link d-flex align-items-center" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#faq2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq2">
                                    <span class="faq-icon mr-3">+</span>
                                    <strong>Lock-in / exit load</strong>
                                </button>
                                <div id="faq2" class="collapse" data-parent="#fusionFaq">
                                    <div class="card card-body">Lock-in periods and exit loads vary by product; exits are processed per PMS agreement. Short-term redemptions may incur an exit fee.</div>
